title: Ep. 599 What are the Clintons Hiding?
description:
What are the Clintons hiding?
http://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2017/11/ex-secret-service-agent-worked-hillary-responds-clinton-mob-attack-know-theyre-hiding-video/
 
The mass exodus from high-tax, liberal, states continues at an alarming rate.



https://nypost.com/2017/04/01/people-are-fleeing-new-york-at-an-alarming-rate/

 
If the tax reform bill passes New York, and other high-tax states, could be in serious trouble.
https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-11-27/in-greenwich-and-manhattan-tax-hike-fears-fuel-talk-of-exodus
 
Nancy Pelosi just destroyed any remaining credibility the Democrats had on ethics and morals.
https://t.co/yi3uO9EzNj
 
The death tax is an economic nightmare for American families and this blue state is trying to make it worse. 
https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/md-politics/congress-may-shrink-the-estate-tax-should-maryland-follow-suit/2017/11/25/3e81cec8-ca54-11e7-b0cf-7689a9f2d84e_story.html
